{"tid":503789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人偷食有毒牡蠣 千葉居民束手無策","createTime":"2017-12-19T08:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T16:09:34.000Z","uid":24140,"like":244,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"fbce287f272d3fd28c7f8ed14925739d2fd83989","tid":503789,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQPJwxEX4AAfQ7h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQPJwxEX4AAfQ7h.jpg&h=f292c579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於千葉縣市川市的江戸川一帶，有大量被棄置的牡蠣空殼（估計達100噸），導致當地居民非常困擾。如果讀者有印象的話，小編在一年前已經寫過這件事。不過，中國人採走江戸川的牡蠣和隨處扔棄空殼已經幾年了，但沒有人能夠阻止，變相鼓勵他們繼續做這件事。據晨間節目《スッキリ！》的報導，一名當地居民指「三年前開始（就看到中國人來採牡蠣），今年七月來這裡的中國人高達一百人。即使我們警告他們，人數也沒有減少。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQPJwxEX4AAfQ7h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQPJwxEX4AAfQ7h.jpg&h=f292c579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在江戶川一帶的牡蠣，牠們的使命並非被人類享用，而是淨化海水。在1950年代，政府為了改善水質污染問題，在江戶川和東京灣養殖牡蠣，至今為止效果非常理想。嚴格上來說，這些牡蠣不適用漁業權的制度，所以中國人在江戶川採牡蠣並不算犯法。<br />\n<br />\n而且，由於他們喜歡即場開蠔，只帶走蠔肉，隨處扔棄空殼，破壞當地環境。由於附近有燒烤場和遊樂場，很多家庭都會經過這段路。單是今年已經有三名小孩被空殼割傷，要立即送院救治。雖然空殼棄置問題嚴重，但警察不能因此拘捕相關的中國人。官方的解釋是，因為牡蠣空殼是自然產物，如同海邊的貝殻一樣，所以不能以亂扔垃圾起訴他們，頂多只可以提點他們要愛護環境。但中國人又會裝聽不懂日文，令日本人束手無策。說到底，居民都無法阻止中國人來採蠔，而為免再發生意外，惟有自發清理牡蠣空殼。<br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/freedom_room/imgs/3/4/34b06578.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Ffreedom_room%2Fimgs%2F3%2F4%2F34b06578.jpg&h=3fdd6983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，據東邦大學理學部的大越健嗣教授所說，這些<span style=\"color: red;\">牡蠣在沒有水質管理的河流生活，應該帶有毒素，並不適宜食用。不過，中國人才不會關心這些牡蠣有沒有毒，對身體有沒有害，只要他們能夠賺錢就行了。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n管理該川流的江戸川河川事務所希望，政府能夠以法律規管採牡蠣和扔空殼的問題。小編希望市川市的居民能夠早日回歸昔日的和平生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://japhub.com/?c=6634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D6634&d=iD56f6Qx1NMVGz9H89OoLu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b1d58276\" target=\"_blank\">https://japhub.com/?c=6634</a>"},{"pid":"dfc3b2aca7be90115043e1729d81cafdb6566938","tid":503789,"uid":62367,"like":136,"dislike":3,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"應該正皮定負皮好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正皮：遲早食死你班蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮：亂咁破壞自然環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9ab62a72024ee8dcbf541906af3acf8f677d45","tid":503789,"uid":55913,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T08:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那狗無可能脫離口腔期"},{"pid":"afe2727e84daa879975e3b79feaf3eb4e0c4c304","tid":503789,"uid":34685,"like":173,"dislike":1,"score":172,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T08:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/164523_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F164523_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=572a180d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b25d6f73508c39f0a2e1bd19b7d0870e2377856","tid":503789,"uid":132565,"like":170,"dislike":2,"score":168,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"你估會自己食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係賣比香港打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲可以話係&quot;日本產地直送&quot;"},{"pid":"4ef4708ee329d69175573856d7ca5b35bd63f72f","